| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7894 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8f672425-9e5e-5939-ade3-96f5cc8456fb"
